{"tid":879223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"條命黑到好撚想死","createTime":"2018-10-27T17:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T12:43:30.000Z","uid":209998,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"da0a3eb8dc838fc378e27b6d01ae6c92c3f2071a","tid":879223,"uid":209998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"今年17歲,<br />\n5年前老豆已經開始冇再同我講野,<br />\n早2年同老母離埋婚,我同佢同呀爺呀嫲住<br />\n半年返一次屋企,一返就打到我入院<br />\n15歲開始要食自己,返part time搵錢食飯<br />\n上年呀爺做完心臟手術啱啱退休,<br />\n今年到呀嫲生cancer 呀爺又要出番黎做野<br />\n今年忙dse 冇時間返工 又要擔心屋企2佬<br />\n攪到好大壓力 患上心理病 <br />\n成撚日頭暈 作嘔 冇胃口 失眠 成身冇力<br />\n使過冇胃口到2日唔食野 <br />\n好撚虛弱 隻手成日都凍冰冰<br />\n好撚辛9若<br />\n好黑仔 無論做咩都冇好運<br />\n出街比舊木扑中個頭<br />\n叫外賣d野食冇調味<br />\n打麻雀8圈先開糊<br />\n係屋企都會腳趾反甲<br />\n成日d野都因為運氣 決定所有野<br />\n唔想再做人 好撚想死"},{"pid":"cbe6022d33c7f622268d368fa44a5a27fe654d43","tid":879223,"uid":217289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:51:06.000Z","msg":"有無朋友可以傾訴"},{"pid":"b56cc1c99cdcf4b83660041fe3997d0ffad15c8e","tid":879223,"uid":54528,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老豆 縮埋一舊"},{"pid":"638dc5681c41fa966d461376b9b2189d0754829e","tid":879223,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"好老實講 搵人傾下"},{"pid":"034b6109f58e43fb1ca76d14203d444fb5023bbf","tid":879223,"uid":58089,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"00後😂😂😂"},{"pid":"33d8384c4d2fc146450e893d1802677aaecd81f2","tid":879223,"uid":202409,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"做多D善事啦。樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0fbf6891ce7611835cd85622a9b88cf1fac5d6","tid":879223,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"有無搵社工呀&hellip;<br />\n17歲人，搵人幫手呀"},{"pid":"8a0d55aacbd07a9295d0e2b0cea90ca83c044678","tid":879223,"ui